snippet.title: Knight's Retreat - PC Gameplay (Steam)
snippet.description:
A chess game without any chess. Rearrange your troops to bring your best Knights back to your Kingdom in an abstract medieval world.

Knight's Retreat (C) Minimol Games
Steam page: https://store.steampowered.com/app/1261700/Knights_Retreat/
Also available for Tilt Five (as free DLC), PS4, Xbox One and Nintendo Switch
